{"tid":2486564,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點解連登咁抗拒叫人做老師","createTime":"2021-04-13T03:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T04:12:26.000Z","uid":1734,"like":13,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"c56c5b2c7109259ff62181f7f09ca24c00d49c4f","tid":2486564,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:26:05.000Z","msg":"個人係某一個項目有好高成就好有才華 自自然然可以教人叫做老師 好似李榮浩老師 王祖藍老師咁 唔明點解要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2624182bae9f6ea0c1f7de744072d5ec2194d958","tid":2486564,"uid":396755,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"好支那"},{"pid":"a52ffeb055bb07cf6928646458134a5865006a0e","tid":2486564,"uid":232229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"31b68ed82a4b6cb01ef519ddfca21c8873da7268","tid":2486564,"uid":1315,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"姜b老師😍😍🥰"},{"pid":"0b08091518020017bcb598f6fedd9b75b65d0a82","tid":2486564,"uid":122134,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"無抗拒<br />\n佢拍戲拍得好 又親身上陣<br />\n又靚仔, 我都係照叫湯告老師"},{"pid":"47a3bc08ee59bf0b66846078f51f5159353ab2d1","tid":2486564,"uid":117837,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"陶傑：亂叫老師<br />\n<br />\n不知何時起，大陸民間時興把看似有幾分學問的中老年男子，不論親疏，都叫「老師」。<br />\n<br />\n余秋雨叫余老師，易中天叫易老師。就是艾未未，沒敢叫，大佬呀，清末民國，叫得老師，是要有正式的拜師儀式的：敬一盞茶，用紅盤子，盛一把間尺，恭敬奉上，禮成之後，做學生的還要掏腰包擺一桌拜師宴。<br />\n<br />\n「天地君親師」，做老師，是很嚴肅的名份，「一日為師，終身為父」，稱一個人做老師，要跟叫一個人做爸爸一樣慎重。你會在街上隨便叫一個戴眼鏡而面有鬍子的男人做爸爸嗎？<br />\n<br />\n但大陸上見一個似有點學識的人，即男簇女擁，好似花果山上的眾小猴拉着回家的齊天大聖般叫「老師」。眾小猴叫孫悟空做爺爺，是真的有名份，「老師」沒有。<br />\n<br />\n香港的一些學者和自命的知識份子，飄飄然的很享受北上大陸時被稱「老師」的感覺，他們覺得在香港特區，中環AO、食環官僚、商場師奶，只識崇拜謝霆鋒，從來不把「讀書人」當人，一過羅湖橋，難得老師前老師後的一片熱衷，很多愛國愛民的特區文人，流下了熱淚。<br />\n<br />\n小心呀，一翻臉，學生也可以鬥爭老師的，文革的宋要武，不是把老師活活打死了麼。<br />\n<br />\n陶傑"},{"pid":"ec3c61ef907b1abfa1f83849f6c3035c705c41e4","tid":2486564,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"老屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2a64245d257b27fbf2b242b882e96656aeb57b","tid":2486564,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"2624182bae9f6ea0c1f7de744072d5ec2194d958","tid":2486564,"uid":396755,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"好支那"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"咁返學都咁叫啦"},{"pid":"01b987c44bc0a92458f3aa73cf17fc6047f2ec08","tid":2486564,"uid":393145,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"樓主喺出post方面<br />\n有好高成就 好有才華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我會尊稱你做濕鳩老師"},{"pid":"65b260f4bdf5209c4150e4bbcd512570b66c3335","tid":2486564,"uid":56546,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"本身諗緊點解個post咁撚鳩, 咁重支那味<br />\n<br />\n一睇邊個開post就即刻明白曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又輕鬆袋5毫"},{"pid":"352dc8960c785a12fc9f64539fe90740d923d5b5","tid":2486564,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b987c44bc0a92458f3aa73cf17fc6047f2ec08","tid":2486564,"uid":393145,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"樓主喺出post方面<br />\n有好高成就 好有才華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我會尊稱你做濕鳩老師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:40:37.000Z","msg":"可以咁"},{"pid":"80e6bb25f5bd9ad7611d7b02d5e60c89034e20a9","tid":2486564,"uid":375948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b08091518020017bcb598f6fedd9b75b65d0a82","tid":2486564,"uid":122134,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"無抗拒<br />\n佢拍戲拍得好 又親身上陣<br />\n又靚仔, 我都係照叫湯告老師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:40:57.000Z","msg":"笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555b30b0ffaacedacc0655c463887a2c8a2ca72c","tid":2486564,"uid":186755,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:41:49.000Z","msg":"思覺老師"},{"pid":"694a460d5af0b0de739436b875696c9d22d85607","tid":2486564,"uid":99700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"濕鳩老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba502b358648eb9c92c73d2cdbcf65b8991eabf","tid":2486564,"uid":393512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:42:29.000Z","msg":"Gem老師😍😍"},{"pid":"aa11915b200452d39521187caf9f7e10eef1cd6d","tid":2486564,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2624182bae9f6ea0c1f7de744072d5ec2194d958","tid":2486564,"uid":396755,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"好支那"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"樓主係江西吉安出世，係汕頭职业技术学院计算机系毕业"},{"pid":"4af374b941e34b275b69c05d96119c11fa5bf0dc","tid":2486564,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555b30b0ffaacedacc0655c463887a2c8a2ca72c","tid":2486564,"uid":186755,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:41:49.000Z","msg":"思覺老師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8939d2be8b5203456fbdf883f95c5cf32caba9","tid":2486564,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"694a460d5af0b0de739436b875696c9d22d85607","tid":2486564,"uid":99700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"濕鳩老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c705ec331bda1b6dfc0cfdd2b3b0cc2c0